dct_title_s: Chart of Cooks River in the N.W. part of America
dct_description_sm: Map of the Cooks River and also showing Capt. Cook's discoveries in Prince William Sound and the Cook Inlet at the head of Cooks River. The map features a time-dated sea track and anchor points of the H.M.S. Resolution over the period May 10-June 9, 1788.
Chart of Cooks River in the north west part of America.
Relief is shown by pictorially and bathymetric soundings.
Coordinates approximate and based on Greenwich meridian.
